Project name: E-commerce Analytics Simulator

Features:
- Load analytics data from CSV or via HTTP (API).
- Filter by date or date range: --start 2025-01-01 --end 2025-01-31. (input from Terminal) 
# think what else can be provided by user, is it enough?  user will also choose metics for analytics
- Compute key KPIs:
   - Sessions / Users
   - Orders / Revenue
   - Conversion Rate ( needed: orders, sessions)
   - Average Order Value (AOV) (revenue, orders)
   - Repeat Customer Rate ( users with ≥2 distinct order_days ÷ ordering users)
   - Returning Customer Share ( orders by returning customers ÷ total orders)
   - Customer Lifetime Value = mean(order_value per user)
   - Breakdowns: group by day/week/month, device, traffic_source.
   - Export results to reports/ as JSON or CSV.

Using Pandas, external librarties, OOP, creation of classes, debugging featuers(errors)
